communications.communication:
To Whom It May Concern:

Pursuant to the Texas Public Information Act, I hereby request the following records:

Please provide me with P.O.s, requisition requests, or any form used to request the purchase of items  for the McLennan County Jail and The Jack Harwell Detention Center for the following,

January the 1st 2017 until December 31st, 2017
January the 1st 2018 until December 31st, 2018
January the 1st 2019 until December 31st, 2019, to include the takeover of the Jack Harwell Detention Center in September 2019
January the 1st 2020 until December 31st, 2020
January the 1st 2021 until December 31st, 2021
January the 1st 2022 until December 31st, 2022
January the 1st 2023 until November 28th, 2023

The requested documents will be made available to the general public, and this request is not being made for commercial purposes.

In the event that there are fees, I would be grateful if you would inform me of the total charges in advance of fulfilling my request. I would prefer the request filled electronically, by e-mail attachment if available or CD-ROM if not.

Thank you in advance for your anticipated cooperation in this matter. I look forward to receiving your response to this request within 10 business days, as the statute requires.

Sincerely,

Bernadette Feazell

To Whom It May Concern:

Pursuant to the New York Freedom of Information Law, I hereby request the following records:

High resolution videos or image frames from all traffic cameras listed on this website:

https://webcams.nyctmc.org/multiview2.php

I specifically request all footage from 1st Ave and 14th Street, on the date December 19, 2023 from 9:30AM to 10:30AM.

The requested documents will be made available to the general public, and this request is not being made for commercial purposes.

In the event that there are fees, I would be grateful if you would inform me of the total charges in advance of fulfilling my request. I would prefer the request filled electronically, by e-mail attachment if available or CD-ROM if not.

Thank you in advance for your anticipated cooperation in this matter. I look forward to receiving your response to this request within 5 business days, as the statute requires.

Sincerely,

David Schultz

communications.communication:
To Whom It May Concern:

Pursuant to the California Public Records Act, I hereby request the following records:

On 2023-08-09 around 5PM, CVPD responded to a call for service categorized as a "Domestic Dispute two subjects seen at the bus stop together no dv seen " near  45 north broadway Avenue.  The incident number is CVL67832.  I am looking for any call detail log, incident report ( including a narrative summary), investigatory report, arrest report, or log of drone activity for this event.  If a stop or search was performed, please provide any records created as part of that search.

The requested documents will be made available to the general public, and this request is not being made for commercial purposes.

In the event that there are fees, I would be grateful if you would inform me of the total charges in advance of fulfilling my request. I would prefer the request filled electronically, by e-mail attachment if available or CD-ROM if not.

Thank you in advance for your anticipated cooperation in this matter. I look forward to receiving your response to this request within 10 calendar days, as the statute requires.

Sincerely,

Dhruv Mehrotra
